def: A carbohydrate of the glucose group found in the thickenedendosperm of certain seeds, and extracted as yellow sirup having asweetish-bitter taste.
Any organ of an animal having a structure adapted to produce aratting sound.
Any plectognath fish that dilates itself, as the bur fish,puffer, or diodon.
One who complies with prevailing opinions, whatever they maybe; a timeserver.Timepleasers, flatterers, foes to nobleness. Shak.
Pain in the muscles; muscular rheumatism or neuralgia.

Large fenders hung over a vessel's side to protect it inhandling a cargo. Totten.(b) One of a pair of timbers or bars, usually arranged so as to forman inclined plane, as form a wagon to a door, along which anything ismoved by sliding or rolling.(c) One of a pair of horizontal rails or timbers for supportinganything, as a boat, a barrel, etc.
Of or pertaining to the genus Meleagris.
Capable of being renewed; as, a lease renewable at pleasure.Swift.
